NAME
    median - calculate the median value of a sample 
 
SYNOPSIS
    #include <acme.h>
    static inherit AcmeStat;
    #include AcmeStatInc
 
    float median( float *sample );
 
DESCRIPTION
    Returns the median value in a sample.  This is actually just
    an alias for the 50th percentile.
 
EXAMPLE
    median( ({ 1, 2, 3 }) ) -> 2
 
SEE_ALSO
    mean(A), median(A), mode(A), percentile(A)
 
LAST MODIFIED                               
    980502 Devo
